Hungary’s Jarai Urges Central Bank to Change Policy, MTI Reports

-- B y   E d i t h   B a l a z s
-- 
2011-03-22T13:59:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/hungary-s-jarai-urges-central-bank-to-change-policy-mti-reports.html
Hungary ’s central bank must change
its monetary policy as recent tightening has helped deepen the
economic crisis, state news agency  MTI  reported, citing Zsigmond Jarai, chairman of the central bank’s supervisory board.  The recently appointed members of the rate-setting Monetary
Council are expected to follow this changed policy, Jarai said,
according to MTI.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edith Balazs in Budapest at 
